    "description": "Structured dataset for the Women in Politics in Africa entry. Combines IPU Women in Politics 2025 country-level parliamentary and cabinet shares with the International IDEA / Gender Links Africa Barometer 2024 ten-indicator power cascade, electoral-system interaction figures, and global portfolio context.",
