      "idea_gender_quotas_database": "https://www.idea.int/data-tools/data/gender-quotas-database"
    },
    "notes": [
      "The SSA regional average of 27.1% is the IPU country-unweighted mean as of 1 January 2025.",
      "The population-weighted estimate of approximately 25% is an Open Ordinal derivation combining IPU 2025 country figures with UN Population Division 2024 mid-year estimates across a partial country panel; it is an approximate directional value, not a published statistic.",
      "Power cascade figures are Africa-wide averages across the 54 states where International IDEA / Gender Links report data for a given indicator; not all positions are reported for all countries.",
      "Cabinet and parliament figures for individual countries are both from the IPU 2025 dataset to keep the reference date aligned."
    ]
  },
